Dear Video Conformance Testing AHG members,

This package contains the conformance Bitstream ID=2.

I encoded 31 instead of the originally proposed 4 frames,
since some discussion seemed to indicate that longer 
bitstream are of more use.

Best regards,

Carsten Herpel.
